<% provide(:title, "Features") %>

<div class="page">
<div class="container">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Tabled</strong> makes it easy to track and analyse legislative activity across Europe.</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag("monitor.png", :alt => "monitor", class: "feature_img") %>
        <h2>Monitor</h2>
        <p><strong>NEWSFEED</strong> Keep up with legislative and regulatory proposals from 33 European legislatures, the EU, and hundreds
        of national regulators through a simple yet comprehensive newsfeed.</p>
        <p><strong>ALERTS</strong> Receive brief and timely email updates on the issues that matter most to you.</p>
        <p><strong>RSS</strong> Subscribe to legislative documents to receive updates throughout their lifecycle.</p>
        <p><strong>ACCESS</strong> Readily access official sources and documents.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag("analyse.png", :alt => "analyse", class: "feature_img") %>
        <h2>Analyse</h2>
        <p><strong>SEARCH</strong> Perform powerful keyword searches across 33 languages.</p>
        <p><strong>FILTER</strong> Filter our expansive database of legislative proposals by issue area, jurisdiction, agency, and key dates.</p>
        <p><strong>VISUALISE</strong> View political risk maps based on key pieces of legislation you are following.</p>
        <p><strong>EXPORT</strong> Create and export comprehensive, customisable reports to share.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag("pencil.png", :alt => "collaborate", class: "feature_img") %>
        <h2>Collaborate</h2>
        <p><strong>BOOKMARK</strong> Bookmark and organize priority legislative proposals.</p>
        <p><strong>FLAG</strong> Flag important proposals to other team members.</p>
        <p><strong>COMMENT</strong> Leave comments and notes for colleagues on key pieces of legislation
        your team is following.</p>
        <p><strong>EMBED</strong> Embed our platform into your own website to activate your members or supporters
        on issues that matter most.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2 style="text-align: center">Interested? <%= link_to "Join", signup_path %> our beta or <%= mail_to "kylebuttner@gmail.com", "email us" %>!</h2>
    </div>

    
</div>
</div>